ing, energy-enhancing, and antioxidant properties. This fascinating fungus has been used for centuries in traditional medicine and is now gaining popularity in the global wellness and supplement market.<\/p><\/div>        <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3c5fdb8 elementor-widget elementor-widget-eael-info-box\" data-id=\"3c5fdb8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"eael-info-box.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t        <div class=\"eael-infobox icon-on-left\">\n\t            <div class=\"infobox-content\">\n                    <div class=\"infobox-title-section\">\n                <h2 class=\"title\">Laboratory Setup: <\/h2>            <\/div>\n            <div><p>A controlled lab environment is essential to initiate Cordyceps culture. This includes clean benches, autoclaves for sterilization, incubators, and laminar airflow units. Maintaining sterility during culture transfer and mycelium propagation is crucial for contamination-free growth.<\/p><\/div>        <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b70a5ca elementor-widget elementor-widget-eael-info-box\" data-id=\"b70a5ca\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"eael-info-box.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t        <div class=\"eael-infobox icon-on-left\">\n\t            <div class=\"infobox-content\">\n                    <div class=\"infobox-title-section\">\n                <h2 class=\"title\">Harvesting &amp; Processing: <\/h2>            <\/div>\n            <div><p>After 45\u201360 days of incubation, Cordyceps fruiting bodies are ready to be harvested. They are carefully picked and dried under low temperatures to preserve active compounds. Post-harvest processing includes grading, packaging, and sometimes powdering for supplement use.<\/p><\/div>        <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c7a2809 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"c7a2809\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;animation&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e42337b e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"e42337b\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1c21690 elementor-widget elementor-widget-eael-info-box\" data-id=\"1c21690\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"eael-info-box.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t        <div class=\"eael-infobox icon-on-left\">\n\t            <div class=\"infobox-content\">\n                    <div class=\"infobox-title-section\">\n                <h2 class=\"title\">Substrate Preparation &amp; Inoculation: <\/h2>            <\/div>\n            <div><p class=\"\">The foundation of successful Cordyceps cultivation begins with preparing a nutrient-rich substrate. A mixture of rice, silkworm pupae powder, and mineral nutrients is sterilized and inoculated with pure Cordyceps culture under sterile conditions to kickstart the fungal growth process.<\/p><\/div>        <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-57901b5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-eael-info-box\" data-id=\"57901b5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"eael-info-box.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t        <div class=\"eael-infobox icon-on-left\">\n\t            <div class=\"infobox-content\">\n                    <div class=\"infobox-title-section\">\n                <h2 class=\"title\">Environmental Conditions: <\/h2>            <\/div>\n            <div><p>Cordyceps requires specific growing conditions to flourish. Ideal parameters include temperatures between 18\u201322\u00b0C, 80\u201390% humidity, 12\u201314 hours of light daily, and CO\u2082 regulation. Proper ventilation and clean environments are vital to maximize yields and avoid contamination.<\/p><\/div>        <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-94011db elementor-widget elementor-widget-eael-info-box\" data-id=\"94011db\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"eael-info-box.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t        <div class=\"eael-infobox icon-on-left\">\n\t            <div class=\"infobox-content\">\n                    <div class=\"infobox-title-section\">\n                <h2 class=\"title\">Marketing &amp; Selling Strategies:<\/h2>            <\/div>\n            <div><p>The demand for Cordyceps is rising globally across health, wellness, and fitness sectors. Marketing strategies should focus on its scientifically backed health benefits. You can sell through wellness stores, e-commerce platforms, herbal product retailers, and even export markets. Clear branding and certification (organic, lab-tested) improve customer trust and sales.<\/p><\/div>        <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c57ff40 elementor-widget__width-auto elementor-absolute elementor-hidden-phone ele